===
Frontend Page Routing URI


GET / 								default homepage
GET /men							products for men
GET /women							products for women
GET /children						products for children





===
Backend API URI

---
Product


GET 	/v1/products/:id 					query product that has the id
POST 	/v1/products/						save product
PUT  	/v1/products/:id					update product that has the id
DELETE 	/v1/products/:id					delete product that has the id



---
Category


GET 	/v1/categories/:category_id/products 		query products that belongs to certain category
		option: ? (pagination | filter | sort | search)
GET 	/v1/categories/:category_id					get category by its id
POST	/v1/categories								save category
PUT		/v1/categories/:category_id					update category by its id
DELETE	/v1/categories/:category_id					delete category by its id